{"tid":945483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大墮海情侶 男生斃命後女生亦告不治","createTime":"2018-12-18T02:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T22:53:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":182,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed717919b6f290010cc47cee525e06404f648bc","tid":945483,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"香港大學一對情侶學生，上周一(10日)在西區副食品批發市場對開岸邊墮海﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2UBFO9e﹞，雙雙被送院搶救，24歲男生陳子熙於周四(13日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UBFO9e%EF%B9%9E%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%99%E9%9B%99%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%90%B6%E6%95%91%EF%BC%8C24%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E9%99%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%86%99%E6%96%BC%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%2813%E6%97%A5&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a6c9629e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2UBFO9e﹞，雙雙被送院搶救，24歲男生陳子熙於周四(13日</a>)不治，其19歲姓梁女友，與死神搏鬥7日後，亦延至昨日下午5時33分宣告不治。<br />\n相關新聞：墮海港大男　捐器官遺愛　女友仍命危　出事原因成謎<br />\n<br />\n上周一晚上約10時，2人被發現在西區副食品批發市場對開岸邊墮海，兩名男途人跳落海用水泡套住兩人拯救，水警到場將兩名俱陷昏迷事主救起送院。警方在現場發現兩事主遺下的背囊和鞋，但未有撿獲遺書，正調查他們是蹈海自殺還是意外墮海。<br />\n陳子熙讀歷史系，19歲梁女讀經濟系。兩人出事後一直陷於昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181218/59042440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59042440&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=91303e77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59042440&h=be822e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181218/59042440</a>"},{"pid":"4cccbf53fa6da88c316cd8b61ccc26306f99699b","tid":945483,"uid":79793,"like":605,"dislike":7,"score":598,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"至少可以一齊"},{"pid":"e75ddbba6985792abefcff5b9ff40f10cc7c3b4f","tid":945483,"uid":20241,"like":301,"dislike":6,"score":295,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:4